Primary: [Consistency]
Secondary: [Zone Manipulation]
Board Wipe
Primary: [Disruption]
Secondary: [Payoff/Win-Con]
Mana Rock
Primary: [Ramp]
Secondary: [Consistency]
[Z] ZONE MANIPULATION LAYER (THE MOVEMENT ECONOMY)
Identify all card movement effects.
Examples:

Draw
